<title>BRAZIL: Souza Cruz H1 net rises vs yr ago.</title>
<headline>Souza Cruz H1 net rises vs yr ago.</headline>
<dateline>SAO PAULO 1997-08-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Brazilian cigarette maker Souza Cruz SA released the following January through June financial results.</p>
<p>		 Jan-June 1997	  Jan-June 1996</p>
<p>Net		166.5 million	  96.1 million</p>
<p>Shr Net	  0.54		     0.31</p>
<p>Net Revs	 887.6 million	  815.7 million</p>
<p>Gross Profit   459.9 million	  432.8 million</p>
<p>Oper Net	 182.3 million	   155.1 million</p>
<p>Note: The figures, published in local newspapers, are in Brazilian reais and not adjusted for inflation.</p>
<p>The firm also said it had a net worth of 1.302 billion reais in the first six months compared with 1.31 billion reais.</p>
<p>Souza Cruz also reported an inflation-adjusted net profit of 123.7 million reais in the January-June period versus a 19.3 million-real in the same period last year.</p>
<p>((--James Craig, Sao Paulo newsroom 5511 2485413))</p>
